{"tid":977411,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"從前有一個阿叔同阿嬸","createTime":"2019-01-11T07:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-13T23:36:37.000Z","uid":230714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba46b26a5556542b19938254c5f80466b5acbe5","tid":977411,"uid":230714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:19:14.000Z","msg":"一個叫王傑 一個叫林憶蓮<br />\n2x年前呢兩把滄桑淒怨嘅聲 合唱過慢歌 「還有」快歌 「冬季來的女人」<br />\n30年後 各自出碟 一個經歷起跌「我知道我是一個已經過氣的歌手」隻碟繼續保持佢隻味 <br />\n另一邊Sandy不停追求突破新專輯「0」<br />\n王傑個人真 唱歌從來唔用假音 自己包辦成隻碟作曲同詞 把聲雖然唔再咁高亮好多位見佢照上 啲歌超高質<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdU6OWfQqYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAdU6OWfQqYM&d=3hh%2BA0qHVMPSzoNK472kfsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=70270601\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdU6OWfQqYM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-fhDo9B9dDU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-fhDo9B9dDU&d=3hh%2BA0qHVMPSzoNK472kfsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=b7db9ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-fhDo9B9dDU</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iuvYG6CZep0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiuvYG6CZep0&d=3hh%2BA0qHVMPSzoNK472kfsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=354249b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iuvYG6CZep0</a><br />\n<br />\n林憶蓮把聲唔單止冇退步仲要越嚟越犀利<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6bhPAp-5l0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO6bhPAp-5l0&d=3hh%2BA0qHVMPSzoNK472kfsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ee84e0a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O6bhPAp-5l0</a><br />\n幻覺動物既玄幻 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=emiOWUKxY_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DemiOWUKxY_I&d=3hh%2BA0qHVMPSzoNK472kfsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=2689